# while 循环简单测试
# 测试 while 循环的基本指令序列：JMP, LTI, 条件跳转
# 简单的 while 循环：while i < 5 do i = i + 1 end
# 期望结果: 5
# 参考 luac -l 生成的字节码

.code
LOADI R0, 0          # i = 0
LTI R0, 5, 0         # if i < 5 then skip next JMP (continue loop)
JMP 3                # if i >= 5, jump to RETURN1 (exit loop)
ADDI R0, R0, 1       # i = i + 1 (loop body)
MMBINI R0, 1, 6, 0   # 如果ADDI失败，用元方法：R0 = R0 + 1, TM_ADD=6
JMP -5               # jump back to condition check (LTI instruction)
RETURN1 R0           # return i (should be 5)
.end
